* Iron Raptor could feel Prowl's embrace around her but she was suddenly tense when he had banked up, she snapped her own head towards the ground and saw the tree that Prowl and herself had barely missed. A shocked feeling went through her but then a smile began to develop on her lips, this had happened because they had been destructed. She chuckled to herself and shock her head, in a sense it was sort of funny. Both to preoccupied to notice where they were going, a dangerous concept when one was trying to fly.
She then though that it would be better if she didn't kiss the designated flyer when he was higher then 5 feet off the ground, it was to distracting and dangerous. But she still chuckled, until Prowl kissed her again.
Iron Raptor didn't want to break from the kiss but she had better before something else happened that they couldn't react fast enough to avoid, she broke from him but kept her face close.
With a smile and slight nod she answered him.*

" I think we'd better."
